data.description: Spacious two-story 5/3.5 home with a well-laid-out kitchen that combines functionality and style. The granite countertops, bar seating area and efficient storage make meal preparation a breeze, while the adjoining dining area is perfect for hosting gatherings. With a master bedroom on the main floor and additional bedrooms upstairs, along with a large flex room, this home offers flexibility and privacy for everyone. Situated on a large corner lot, there is plenty of outdoor space for relaxation and entertainment. Conveniently located near schools, shopping, and transportation routes, this home provides convenience and accessibility.
